Short summary of third party components used in Parley for Android.
Many thanks to the authors of all these free software components!

---
Uses MobVoc for kvtml parsing and data structures
Copyright (C) 2008 Michael Hofer mobvoc [at] unglaublich.priv.at
Originally released under GPLv2  
---
Uses the KXML2 library for XML parsing
Copyright (C) 2002,2003, Stefan Haustein, Oberhausen, Rhld., Germany
Originally released under a BSD license
---
Uses UserTask for easy UI threading.
Copyright (C) 2008 Google Inc.
Originally released under the Apache License, Version 2 (see 
http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0 for details)
---
Uses ArabicShaper for proper rendering of Arabic strings
Copyright (C) 2008 Ahmed Essam
Copyright (C) 2009 Abdull B <x2android@gmail.com>
Unlicensed.
